quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  18,84,"Toto efwe khwamura obulai muno khushialo, ne nikhumuwa injila yokhunyoola buli eshindu."
  18,85,"Mana naloonda injila."
  18,86,"Okhuula shingala yoola ebukwe weliuba, yalinyola liheranga khusebere eya amatoyi amanji. Awo nanyoola Abandu. Nikhuboola mbu: “Ewe Dhul’karnain, bahelesie eshinyasio nohomba obakholele obulayi.”"
  18,87,"Naboola mbu: “Ulia owakhola obubii, khwitsa okhumuwa eshinyasio, mana alikalusibwa khu Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi, naye alimuhelesia eshinyasio eshibii muno."
  18,88,"Ne ulia owasuubila mana nakhola ebikhole ebilayi, alanyoola omurungo omulayi, nafu khwitsa okhumuboolela amakhuwa kefu amangu."
  18,89,"Mana naloonda injila."
  18,90,"Okhula shingala yoola weliuba lirulilanga (mumbo), yalinyola nilirulilanga khubandu abalakhwarereraho eshishinjilo shiokhubekalila okhurulana ninalio tawe."
  18,91,"Ne shinga endio khwali nikhumanyile obulayi amakhuwa koosi kayali ninako."
  18,92,"Mana naloonda injila."
  18,93,"Okhula shingala yoola hakari wetsingulu tsibili, yanyoola inyuma watsio abandu balawulilanga amakhuwa tawe."
  18,94,"Nibaboola mbu: “Ewe Dhul-Karnain, toto Yaajuj nende Maajuj, bakholanga obuononi khushyalo. Kho khukhwelesie omurungo ore eshikalilo hakari wefu ninabo?”"
  18,95,"Naboola mbu: “Kalia ka Nyasaye wanje Omulesi yandinyisiliamwo ni amalayi muno. Kho, mukhoonye nende amaani, ndalara hakari wenyu ninabo eshikalilo eshisiro."
  18,96,"Munderere ebitonye bieshichuma.” okhula shingala yetsusia obwiyangu buli hakari wetsingulu tsibili etso, naboola mbu: ‘‘Bwaane (omulilo)” okhula shingala yakhola eshichuma esho omulilo, naboola mbu: ‘‘Nderere ishaba isalulushe enzushe khuno.”"
  18,97,"Mana shibanyala okhushinina bashiambuka, nohomba okhuyabamo obwina tawe."